2 File Format
*************

Each line in the file should be in a ‘KEY=VALUE’ format, with one entry
per line.  This package does not invoke a shell to interpret the file,
so most shell-isms will not work.  However, as a convenience, the env
file may:

   • Define simple shell-like variables
   • Use existing environment variables
   • Tildes are expanded if they are the first character of the value


